701436f-a.title: Bronx: Matthews Avenue - Rhinelander Avenue
701436f-a.text:
Mntthews Avenue, east side, north from Rhinelander
to Bronxdale Avenues. The house in the center is number
1913 Bronxdale Avenue.
June 22, 1940
P. L. Sperr
